title: The Complete Published Ellen G. White Writings
description:
*NOTES*
This software contains all Ellen G. White published material including Books (100+), Periodicals (78), Pamphlets (150+), Manuscript Releases (27), Miscellaneous Collections (11), and Biographical Books (7). The readme says Feburary 2002 but the software appears much "older" (Win95/98 vintage).

*Features*
Full Text Search; Topical search (Comprehensive Index); Scripture Index; KJV Bible; Bibliography; and Tutorials on how to use the software (Folio Views 4.2 [Build 316])


Enjoy, Seed, and Share!
